    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is presented in honest, well-cared-for condition. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor, unavoidable road peppering on the lower front valance. The interior features Parchment NuLuxe seating that remains supple and free of tears or heavy wear; it has been kept in a smoke-free and pet-free environment. All power options, including the panoramic sunroof, heated/ventilated seats, and the 12.3-inch multimedia display, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 runs quietly and efficiently, backed by a full service history performed at the local dealership. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, new cabin air filters, and a set of four Michelin tires with approximately 80% tread remaining. The brakes feel firm and the suspension provides the signature smooth Lexus ride without any rattles or knocks. This is a turn-key luxury SUV ready for its next chapter.",
